name: MPRemoteCommandHandlerStatus
desc: Constants indicating the status of a command.

items.name: case noSuchContent
items.desc: The requested command couldn’t execute because its required content isn’t available.

items.name: case noActionableNowPlayingItem
items.desc: The requested command couldn’t execute because no Now Playing item is available.

items.name: case deviceNotFound
items.desc: The requested command couldn’t execute because a required device isn’t available.

items.name: case commandFailed
items.desc: The requested command failed to execute.
